    "description": "Pack in the veg with this Japanese-inspired, low-calorie noodle stir fry. Pan-fry mushrooms until golden, then add mooli slaw and edamame for a pop of colour. Finish with a garlic and ginger spiked teriyaki sauce, toasted cashews for crunch and serve with a fried egg on top. 3 or more of your 5/day",
